<br>
This is actually the kind of uncool behavior that may be reported to the GM's and result in someone being removed from the game. None of us may really wish to be that mean to anyone ourselves and cry foul to the powers that be - most of us aren't reallly all that concerned with the loot anyway - but don't be afraid to tell this guy or anyone else to back off.<br>
<br>
Galadria<br>
